songs.title: Long ride
songs.lyrics:
I need to get right
It's a long ride
The drugs help me hide
The drugs help me hide, oh

I need to confide
True loves hard to find
I wait for her to come find me
I’ll ever pay the flights
I need to confide
True loves hard to find
I wait for her to come find me
I'll ever pay the flights

Okay, it's been a long ride
Still the beginning of the ride
I’m getting high before the flights
L.A.X to the Chi
Memories on my mind
Been reflecting all my life
Something don't feel right
Down deep inside
I'm scared of my own demise
I need to confide to the love of my life, life
It's getting dark outside
